{"data":[{"date":"23:24 10/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 1 trong 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1eddi ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch t\u1eeb NHM song V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Chi\u1ec1u 10/8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Van-Quyet-giai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-Olympic-Viet-Nam-len-duong-du-A-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft: \"N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec c\u1ea3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3. Vi\u1ec7c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea7u t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m vinh d\u1ef1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Anh chia s\u1ebb: \"L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u00f5 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00eda. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh, gi\u00e0nh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#4C4947\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5348","checkdouble":"194206"},{"date":"23:24 10/08","title":"C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao \"v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\" d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/10/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao \"v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\"?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 1 trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ea1t ra kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 ASIAD cho anh.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Minh-Vuong-duoc-goi-bo-sung-len-tuyen-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/8, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb VFF, khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c thu d\u1ecdn h\u00e0nh trang t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n bay di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb nhanh v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean\u00a0Goal.com\u00a0sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3 h\u1edfi: \"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u00e1ng nay, em c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Em th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i em s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai 1/8. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" open=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5347","checkdouble":"194207"},{"date":"23:36 10/08","title":"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd \u2018Messi m\u1edbi\u2019, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/phot-lo-messi-moi-olympic-indonesia-trieu-tap-sao-u40-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/XT5gRGy6Ah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n\u00a0Olympic Indonesia t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alberto Goncalves, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 38 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c Brazil. Anh \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Indonesia trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sriwijaya. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 6 l\u1ea7n 'khai h\u1ecfa'.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Alberto Goncalves \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alberto Goncalves, m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 Lan, Stefano Lilipaly v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany Ardiyasa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \"Messi m\u1edbi\" Egy Maulana Vikri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, Indonesia n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i Palestine, Hong Kong (TQ), \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5346","checkdouble":"194209"},{"date":"23:55 10/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/truyen-thong-nhat-ban-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t t\u1eebng \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i, n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u01b0\u1edbc\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c v\u1eeba l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Asiad 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal, Olympic Pakistan. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u0169ng xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Truyen-thong-Nhat-Ban-noi-gi-ve-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 t\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian qua. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qoly c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd n\u00e0y m\u00f4 t\u1ea3: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi m\u00e0 trong tay HLV Hajime th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Olympic 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 v\u1ecb \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u1ecd\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Qoly vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 sau: \u00a0\u201cTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf K-League. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i J-League 2 nh\u01b0ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/10/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5345","checkdouble":"194210"},{"date":"00:26 11/08","title":"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/6/12/hlv-truong-clb-thai-son-nam-noi-gi-khi-vao-chung-ket-futsal-cac-clb-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Miguel Rodrigo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m 6-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Lebanon, Bank of Beirut.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/12/tan-hlv-miguel-rodrigo-futsal-viet-nam-van-thua-thai-lan.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miguel Rodrigo t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn 3-1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam ch\u01a1i b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 ghi li\u1ec1n 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Qu\u1ed1c H\u01b0ng (29') v\u00e0 c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn (32', 35' v\u00e0 36') gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 5-3. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 6-5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u1ede c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 2017 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Miguel Rodrigo, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 cho hay: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3-1. S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p CLB \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Iran, Mes Sungun Varzaghan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CLB Nafit Al-wasat 3-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h ng\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight: Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 6-5 Beirut<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/10/Thai-Son-Nam-FC-6-5-Bank-of-Beirut.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5344","checkdouble":"194214"},{"date":"19:25 10/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 10/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 Man Utd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Mourinho ng\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Diem-tin-bongda24hvn-toi-ngay-108---Tin-bong-da-24h-moi-nhat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Jose Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c leo thang v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t khi BL\u0110 MU y\u00eau c\u1ea7u HLV Jose Mourinho ng\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi mua s\u1eafm v\u00e0 n\u00ean khai th\u00e1c nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 trong tay c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1eadp trung cho c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Leo Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barcelona<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leo Messi\" title=\"Leo Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/192357-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Leo Messi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Sau khi bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Andreas Iniesta ra \u0111i, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ra ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, vinh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t ki\u00eam huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng Leo Messi. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Sergio Busquets, Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Sergi Roberto.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jamie Vardy ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 108 Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 108 Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-Messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-Barca-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jamie Vardy</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Leicester City, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2022 khi anh 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tr\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n King Power. V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o, Vardy c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i Yerry Mina<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina chinh thuc toi Everton\" title=\"Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Barcelona v\u1eabn g\u00e0i th\u00eam v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i (54 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u2013 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro). Mina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Goodison Park trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Andre Gomes (cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n) v\u00e0 Lucas Digne. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Cac-thu-mon-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-Goc-nhin-ve-gia-tri-thuc-su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Thibaut Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u01a1n th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i khi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4n l\u00ean logo Real Madrid trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft, gi\u1edd th\u00ec Courtois \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a lu\u00f4n post t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay Chelsea tr\u00ean Instagram khi h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u1edf m\u1ee5c comment.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Tottenham chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" title=\"Danny Rose cua Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/Mourinho-len-tieng-vu-MU-mua-Danny-Rose-cua-Tottenham--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Rose</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u00e1c CLB Premier League kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Danny Rose v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Spurs. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5343","checkdouble":"194199"},{"date":"22:09 10/08","title":"Barca v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao kh\u1ee7ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/barca-van-nuoi-hy-vong-so-huu-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Iniesta, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Khi m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Old Trafford, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/barca-van-nuoi-hy-vong-so-huu-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Paul Pogba\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Pogba, Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Old Trafford, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi CLB. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i, song Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i. Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca c\u00f3 Pogba l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, M.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Pogba \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Barca\" title=\"Pogba Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-1008.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca c\u00f3 Pogba l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u1edbi M.U c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Barca \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U nh\u1ea3 Pogba, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Pogba \u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u00f9 Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5342","checkdouble":"194194"},{"date":"23:24 10/08","title":"Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf Stamford Bridge ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Luka Modric c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf Anh, Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric khuy\u00ean Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric khuy\u00ean Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-Mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-Godin-loi-dung-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh Modric khuy\u00ean Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Bernabeu, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea1nh tranh <br>\r\ng\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi d\u00e0n sao tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Luka Modric. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kovacic, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Luka. Anh \u1ea5y vui v\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n khi th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i ra \u0111i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n nhau m\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">\u201cAnh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng London l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, Premier League l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1eafp kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i r\u1ed3i.\u201d \u2013 Modric hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean th\u1eeba kinh nghi\u1ec7m sau 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid n\u0103m 2012.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Kovacic s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ra m\u1eaft ngay \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn derby London g\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Arsenal \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nMateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kovacic t\u1eeb Real c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i mang \u0111\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1D2129;background:\nwhite\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5341","checkdouble":"194208"},{"date":"06:46 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d Michy Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d Valencia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Michy Batshuayi lang b\u1ea1t sang \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh thu\u00ea cho Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 9 b\u00e0n/14 tr\u1eadn.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi Chelsea hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra h\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ebfn Alvaro Morata. Kh\u00f4ng, s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Batshuayi r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c khi anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Chelsea l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB th\u00e0nh London nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t video clip \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0n d\u01a1i. \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d (Batman) l\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t danh c\u1ee7a Batshuayi, trong khi Valencia l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Batshuayi \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Tammy Abraham v\u00e0 Callum Hudson-Odoi, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng trung phong \u0111\u00e0n anh kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5340","checkdouble":"194218"},{"date":"04:32 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n di\u1ec5n ra trong \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Leicester \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 thua c\u1ea3 2 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Ryan Babel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Pogba-thuc-hien-thanh-cong-penalty-cho-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Jose Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i Premier League, Mourinho th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Luke Shaw c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 67 cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 123 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong c\u1ea3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Leicester \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester (th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 8 trong 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gh\u00e9 th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford (h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Premier League, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t (18).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- M.U b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 10 sau 11 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6 (th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 21 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh khi ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6 (th\u1eafng 15, h\u00f2a 6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5339","checkdouble":"194220"},{"date":"05:38 11/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-21-cua-mu-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c Man United \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Leicester City v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Jose Mourinho l\u1eadp danh s\u00e1ch 5 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 cho Manchester United. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, cho t\u1edbi khi chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/M.U-dan-truoc-Leicester-1-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, M.U v\u1eabn h\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea m\u1edbi c\u1ee9u h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, trong th\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Maddison b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester. B\u1eb1ng ma thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Song khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ngai v\u00e0ng Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, xem ra Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean M.U, Jonny Evans \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Leicester h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trong khi 2 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Filip Benkovic v\u00e0 Caglar Soyuncu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n Leicester v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-2-1-cua-MU-truoc-Leicester-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Leicester khi\u1ebfn M.U kh\u00e1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, Leicester nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Cho t\u1edbi chung cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (53,8%). N\u1ebfu Maddison hay Iheanacho nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n h\u01a1n, B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Shaw ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d, Leicester c\u00f9ng Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2m l\u00fd B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e0n. S\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng qua, HLV Mourinho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c k\u00eau than v\u00e0 khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua s\u1eafm kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0o, n\u00f3 lan t\u1ecfa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t tr\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111i c\u00e1i d\u1edbp m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n. T\u00ednh c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mou l\u00e0m cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, M.U lu\u00f4n t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh. Cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu. Th\u1eadt may Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, song h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u\u201d m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Sanchez l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Sanchez tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Sanchez-tran-M.U-vs-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sanchez l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, m\u1ecdi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sanchez \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf. Ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty cho M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, anh c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 cho Romelu Lukaku. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Sanchez l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Leicester khi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, M.U ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 68 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u00edt h\u01a1n 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong t\u1ed1p 4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Sanchez, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Maddison g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, song James Maddison th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. M\u1edbi 21 tu\u1ed5i, ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn t\u1eeb m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 m\u00e0 Ryiad Mahrez \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i song anh tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maddison cua Leicester\" title=\"Maddison cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Maddison-cua-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Maddison c\u1ee7a Leicester t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Demarai Gray, Maddison l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Tr\u00f4ng c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Norwich nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u binh d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i \u201cth\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba\u201d Old Trafford c\u1ee7a M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu De Gea kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n, Maddison \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 45 ph\u00fat. Duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 1996 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5338","checkdouble":"194222"},{"date":"06:08 11/08","title":"\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester, Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19. Sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Wes Morgan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i tr\u00fang tay m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 Daniel Amartey trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Leicester v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch d\u1ed3n M.U v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i\u00a0Leicester 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Leicester t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu s\u1eafc b\u00e9n c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap M.U \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83. Luke Shaw \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy ph\u00fat 90+2 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Chung cu\u1ed9c M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Mourinho-tran-M.U-vs-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRichard Scudamore (Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Premier League) ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 6 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i 3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Anthony Martial, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. Paul Pogba kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i 90 ph\u00fat, Fred c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Leicester r\u1ea5t hay trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5337","checkdouble":"194223"},{"date":"06:37 11/08","title":"Luke Shaw n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Luke Shaw t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Valencia r\u1ed3i Marcos Rojo b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ashley Young ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u1eadu World Cup 2018, c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi HLV Jose Mourinho bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Luke Shaw cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00edch danh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Luke-Shaw-ghi-ban-dau-tien-cho-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Shaw quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Southampton \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho M.U v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 ph\u00fat 90+2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 67 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho M.U tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Southampton n\u0103m 2014, Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Juan Mata, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Leicester.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194220.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194220.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng. Vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sky Sports. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 xoay x\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ng\u1eabm, l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf cho HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Man United v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5336","checkdouble":"194224"}]}